      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2005 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L straight-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS timing. This manual-equipped example is mechanically flawless, with documented preventative subframe reinforcement and rod bearing service already completed. The factory-spec suspension maintains its original geometry with no bushing deflection, ensuring the sharp turn-in and chassis balance the M-division is known for. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the cockpit features pristine Nappa leather and an unblemished dash. Every system, from the variable M-differential lock to the cooling system's expansion tank, has been inspected to ensure it meets the highest operational standards for a purist collector.",
